description:
Smart Charge, a new service brand run by HKT and CLP, aims to offer one-stop and hassle-free electric vehicle (EV) charging solutions for end-users and commercial entities in Hong Kong to meet the increasing market demand. 

It is a challenging and dynamic opportunity for an all rounded marketer to work for this brand which is striving for differentiation and continual growth. 

Your role:

Explore partnership opportunities / initiatives and manage day-to-day partnership operations and logistics;
Nurture long term relationships with key strategic partners to foster consistent support to Smart Living products via joint promotions or events, including lead generation events and external corporate events;
Build and manage scalable partnership programs to drive broad adoption of Smart Charge products and services;
Collaborate with various internal and external parties for planning and executing marketing campaigns, including the planning and execution of operation logistic , advertising and communication tools from concept to implementation;
Ensure marketing messages are synchronized across different business units and monitor  marketing campaigns to ensure communications are streamlined and aligned;
Stay informed of news and marketing activities in  relevant markets.  

To succeed in this role:

University graduate in Marketing, Communications, Business Administration or related disciplines;
Minimum 8 years working experience in Product or Service Marketing and/or related field;
Proven track record of driving partnership strategy, preferably in luxury product industry, prestige members clubs and automotive industries;
Strong business acumen with exceptional logical thinking, highly motivated and presentable
Demonstrated initiative and problem solving skills with a service focus
Excellent communication and interpersonal skills, with ability to work effectively and cross-functionally with people at all levels
Knowledge or interest in automobile industry
Proficiency in both spoken and written English and Cantonese
Candidates with more experience will be considered as Assistant Vice President

If you have the desire for an exciting and rewarding career, please send us your resume immediately, quoting the reference number, your present and expected salary via email to Human Resources.

